  "summary": "ReviewBoard and Djblets library are vulnerable to code execution",
  "details": "An eval() vulnerability exists in Python Software Foundation Djblets version before 0.6.30 and 0.7.0 before 0.7.19 and Beanbag Review Board before 1.7.15 when parsing JSON requests allowing an attacker to execute arbitrary Python code.",
